WEBVTT

00:05:54.887 --> 00:06:00.903
that I can cook, no really, it’s true.

00:06:00.927 --> 00:06:04.767
On a plane, I calm and put kids to sleep.

00:06:06.167 --> 00:06:08.583
It’s a small thing but very vital.

00:06:08.607 --> 00:06:14.503
We should not tell men that
this is your responsibility xyz --

00:06:14.527 --> 00:06:15.823
that is also wrong --

00:06:15.847 --> 00:06:19.663
and not tell girls that you have
to look after things, compromise.

00:06:19.687 --> 00:06:23.503
If we start from here, there will be
a change in society. Totally.

00:06:23.527 --> 00:06:24.740
Isn’t this what you wanted to say?

00:06:24.780 --> 00:06:25.573
MK: Yes.

00:06:25.593 --> 00:06:26.387
Thank you so much Manju ji.

00:06:26.397 --> 00:06:30.157
Please give a big round
of applause for Maju Kapur.